The House of Mirth;;72;;82;;PG;;Lily (Gillian Anderson) is a ravishing socialite who quickly discovers the precariousness of her position when her beauty and charm start attracting unwelcome interest and jealousy. She seeks a wealthy husband and, in trying to conform to social expectations, she misses her chance for real love with Lawrence Selden (Eric Stoltz). Her quest for a husband comes to a scandalous end when she is falsely accused of having an affair with a married man and is rejected by society and her friends.;;History,Drama;;Terence Davies;;2000;;Gillian Anderson,Eric Stoltz,Dan Aykroyd,Eleanor Bron,Terry Kinney,Anthony LaPaglia,Laura Linney,Jodhi May,Elizabeth McGovern;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/house_of_mirth